summary: If your first thought is PewDiePie after learning about the terrorist attack in New Zealand you need to take a break from video...
body:
If your first thought is PewDiePie after learning about the terrorist attack in New Zealand you need to take a break from video games, porn, and YouTube.

If your next thought is to actually go online and defend him; the brain rot has set too deep, seek help.

summary:
Oooof I just LOVE this @avene_sa Soothing Moisture Mask 🧖🏼‍♀️ I do t know what else to say. 

It’s an absolute treat of a mask....
caption:
Oooof I just LOVE this @avene_sa Soothing Moisture Mask 🧖🏼‍♀️ I do t know what else to say.

It’s an absolute treat of a mask. I love having a pamper at least once a week with an exfoliating mask or scrub, followed by this lovely hydrating mask. I apply this by packing it on to my skin, pinning my hair up and letting my skin driiiink this up. And trust me, it does. It’s such an easy mask, you don’t have to remove it. Especially if you leave it on to sink in and just go to bed with it like that. This plumps my skin up with all the goodness it needs.

I just love this it so much. I got mine from clicks in January and it’s still lasting me a while. Love. It.

This works wonders on very dry and sensitive skin.

Have you tried it? What are your thoughts? ✨
